\par }\pard\plain \qj\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\b\f16 mosaic OA}{\b  }{  (MOA) is for use with the Microsoft Windows NT or Windows 95 operating system.  The CDS client software can run happily on Windows 95.   The server software }{\i can}{
 also run on Windows 95 but we recommend that you run it only on Windows NT.  This package contains the Central Data Server software.  It may be used in conjunction with a separately-released workstation software piece known as \ldblquote 
Mosaic OA Development and Runtime\rdblquote .  It may also be used with separately released workstation software product know as \ldblquote Mosaic OA CDS ODBC Driver\rdblquote .
\par 
\par }\pard\plain \s2\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\outlinelevel1\adjustright \b\i\f1\cgrid {{\*\bkmkstart _Toc389469600}Compatability{\*\bkmkend _Toc389469600}
\par }\pard\plain \qj\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\cgrid {\b\f16 mosaic OA  }{provides a migration path from Pinnacle Plus Release 4/5.  The CDS table data is compatible with Release 1.1 and 1.2.  No data conversion is required to upgrade from }{\b\f16 
mosaic OA}{\b  }{Release 1.1 to }{\b\f16 mosaic OA}{\b  }{Release 1.4, simply import your table data after exporting with Release 1.  Or, verify that the field tables are the same and remove the ddtime file(s).  }{\b There is }{\b\i no conversion}{\b 
 for moving from Release 1.3 to 1.4.}{   Simply install the new software and access the old data without any data changes!   This server package may be used with MOA runtime package version 1.3.7 or later.
\par }\pard\plain \s1\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\outlinelevel0\adjustright \b\f1\fs28\kerning28\cgrid {{\*\bkmkstart _Toc389469601}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc316106367}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc316106689}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc316107074}{\*\bkmkstart _Toc316176556}
