\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {06-05-96 CDSCL.DLL changes (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Fixed bug in rollback of deletes, as per Bruce Oscarson in R1V3.  This bug caused server to crash during rollback and recovery.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Fix reentrancy problem in debugging code.  This made it possible to use cdscl.lib for prcaptur.exe.
\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {04-23-96 CDSV.exe Enhancements  (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Added comparators like, not_like, and is_not_null to PQL for support of ODBC interface.   These comparators are usable through the ASCII interface only (not from OFB).
\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 {\*\pn \pnlvlcont\ilvl0\ls0\pnrnot0\pndec }\adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {04-23-96 CDSSTAT.exe Enhancement   (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Added -D command line option to tell cdsv to reset debugsw and mcn tracing from ddproj.ini values for CDS_DEBUGSW and CDS_NWLIB.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Changed usage statement for cdsstat in \\moa\\lib\\err_5800.
\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {04-18-96 CDSV Enhancements (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Added more information to messages about failures of recovery during rollforward from the recover log.   Put more into the event log message to compensate for not having a core dump.   Updated \\moa\\lib\\err_5800 and cds\\rollfor.c
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Improved response to shutdown requests.  Don\rquote t open a new listen if Sv_running = False. changes in servnt.c.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Got rid of DNIX code in ccb.c
\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {04-04-96 CDSV Enhancements (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Enhanced the optimizer to recognize comparisons to empty string values for fields in indexes.  Always read the minimum or zero index and base records.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Enhanced the optimizer to recognize IS_MISSING criteria for fields in indexes.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Added more explanation of the optimizer\rquote s index choices when the -E option is used
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Added printing of number of index and base records read when the Explanation level option is relevant and set non-zero.   See CDSNOTES.doc.
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}Increased the maximum number of variables in a criteria expression from 100 to 255.
\par }\pard\plain \s31\sb240\sa60\keepn\widctlpar\brdrb\brdrs\brdrw15\brsp20 \adjustright \b\f1\cgrid {1-19-96 CDS clients enhancement (CDSCL.DLL) (s)
\par {\pntext\pard\plain\s32 \f14\fs20\cf10\cgrid \loch\af14\dbch\af0\hich\f14 \'fc\tab}}\pard\plain \s32\fi-360\li360\widctlpar{\*\pn \pnlvlblt\ilvl0\ls6\pnrnot0\pncf10\pnf14\pnstart1\pnindent360\pnhang{\pntxtb \'fc}}\ls6\adjustright \f1\fs20\cgrid {
Created new dynamic link library, cdscl.dll for all cds clients except rt.  New subdirectory \\moa\\src\\cdscl, new src\\cdscl.mak.
\par }\pard\plain \s29\qj\keep\keepn\widctlpar\adjustright \f2\fs18\cgrid {
\par }}